    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Patients and doctors",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.34,
      "endTime": 9.45
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What are patients looking for when they visit the doctor?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.46,
      "endTime": 14.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "This is a sceptical age,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 14.79,
      "endTime": 16.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but although our faith in many of the things in which our forefathers fervently believed has weakened,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.94,
      "endTime": 23.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "our confidence in the curative properties of the bottle of medicine remains the same as theirs.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "endTime": 30.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This modern faith in medicines is proved by the fact",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 30.52,
      "endTime": 34.22,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "that the annual drug bill of the Health Services is mounting to astronomical figures.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34.23,
      "endTime": 40.5,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and shows no signs at present of ceasing to rise.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.51,
      "endTime": 45.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The majority of the patients attending the medical out-patients departments of our hospitals feel that",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 45.25,
      "endTime": 51.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they have not received adequate treatment unless they are able to carry home with them",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.22,
      "endTime": 56.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "some tangible remedy in the shape of a bottle of medicine,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.22,
      "endTime": 60.28
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "a box of pills, or a small jar of ointment,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 60.29,
      "endTime": 64.2
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and the doctor in charge of the department is only too ready to provide them with these requirements.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.21,
      "endTime": 70.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Too",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "也"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "There is no quicker method of disposing of patients than by giving them what they are asking for,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 70.98,
      "endTime": 77.29,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and since most medical men in the Health Services are overworked",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.3,
      "endTime": 81.57,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and have little time for offering time-consuming and little-appreciated advice on such subjects as diet,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 81.58,
      "endTime": 89.09
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "right living, and the need for abandoning bad habits etc.,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 89.1,
      "endTime": 93.8
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the bottle, the box, and the jar are almost always granted them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 93.81,
      "endTime": 99.02,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Nor is it only the ignorant and ill-educated person who has such faith in the bottle of medicine.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 99.03,
      "endTime": 105.78,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It is recounted of Thomas Carlyle that when he heard of the illness of his friend, Henry Taylor,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 105.79,
      "endTime": 112.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "he went off immediately to visit him,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.98,
      "endTime": 115.98
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "carrying with him in his pocket what remained a bottle of medicine formerly prescribed for an indisposition of Mrs. Carlyle's.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 115.99,
      "endTime": 126.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Carlyle was entirely ignorant of what the bottle in his pocket contained,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 126.16,
      "endTime": 131.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "of the nature of the illness from which his friend was suffering,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 131.22,
      "endTime": 135.01,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and of what had previously been wrong with his wife,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 135.02,
      "endTime": 138.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but a medicine that had worked so well in one form of illness would surely be of equal benefit in another,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 138.7,
      "endTime": 145.87,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and comforted by the thought of the help he was bringing to his friend,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 145.88,
      "endTime": 150.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "he hastened to Henry Taylor's house.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 150.16,
      "endTime": 153.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "House",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "房子"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "History does not relate whether his friend accepted his medical help, but in all probability he did.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 153.66,
      "endTime": 160.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The great advantage of taking medicine is that it makes no demands on the taker",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 160.74,
      "endTime": 165.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "beyond that of putting up for a moment with a disgusting taste,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 165.65,
      "endTime": 169.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and that is what all patients demand of their doctors--to be cured at no inconvenience to themselves.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 169.86,
      "endTime": 174.86,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
